{"ja419:0.1":"Jataka ","ja419:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","ja419:0.3":"Kaccanivagga ","ja419:0.4":"3. Sulasajataka ","ja419:1.1":"“Idam suvannakayuram, ","ja419:1.2":"mutta veluriya bahu; ","ja419:1.3":"Sabbam harassu bhaddante, ","ja419:1.4":"manca dasiti savaya”. ","ja419:2.1":"“Oropayassu kalyani, ","ja419:2.2":"ma balham paridevasi; ","ja419:2.3":"Na caham abhijanami, ","ja419:2.4":"ahantva dhanamabhatam”. ","ja419:3.1":"“Yato sarami attanam, ","ja419:3.2":"yato pattasmi vinnutam; ","ja419:3.3":"Na caham abhijanami, ","ja419:3.4":"annam piyataram taya. ","ja419:4.1":"Ehi tam upaguhissam, ","ja419:4.2":"karissanca padakkhinam; ","ja419:4.3":"Na hi dani puna atthi, ","ja419:4.4":"mama tuyhanca sangamo”. ","ja419:5.1":"“Na hi sabbesu thanesu, ","ja419:5.2":"puriso hoti pandito; ","ja419:5.3":"Itthipi pandita hoti, ","ja419:5.4":"tattha tattha vicakkhana. ","ja419:6.1":"Na hi sabbesu thanesu, ","ja419:6.2":"puriso hoti pandito; ","ja419:6.3":"Itthipi pandita hoti, ","ja419:6.4":"lahum attham vicintika. ","ja419:7.1":"Lahunca vata khippanca, ","ja419:7.2":"nikatthe samacetayi; ","ja419:7.3":"Migam punnayateneva, ","ja419:7.4":"sulasa sattukam vadhi. ","ja419:8.1":"Yodha uppatitam attham, ","ja419:8.2":"na khippamanubujjhati; ","ja419:8.3":"So hannati mandamati, ","ja419:8.4":"corova girigabbhare. ","ja419:9.1":"Yo ca uppatitam attham, ","ja419:9.2":"khippameva nibodhati; ","ja419:9.3":"Muccate sattusambadha, ","ja419:9.4":"sulasa sattukamiva”ti. ","ja419:10.1":"Sulasajatakam tatiyam. "}